name: websdk-cdn
description: Zoom sample app for web client WebSDK

scripts.start: set NODE_ENV=development && set BABEL_ENV=development && webpack serve --config webpack.config.dev.js
scripts.https: set NODE_ENV=development && set BABEL_ENV=development && webpack serve --config webpack.config.dev.js --https
scripts.corp: set NODE_ENV=development && set BABEL_ENV=development && node corp.js --corp
